        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0007",
      "text": "7.1.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        118.22,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0008",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        106.97,
        186.53,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0009",
      "text": "The Process Login (PRLI) ELS request shall be used to establish the operating environment between",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.0,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0010",
      "text": "a group of related processes at the originating Nx_Port and a group of related processes at the re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.97,
        540.14,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0011",
      "text": "sponding Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.97,
        178.2,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0012",
      "text": "Establishing the operating environment may include the establishment of image pairs and the ex-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.13,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0013",
      "text": "change of Service Parameters.  The establishment of image pairs is FC-4 independent and is system",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        539.87,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0014",
      "text": "structure dependent.  The exchange of Service Parameters is FC-4 dependent, and if required by a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.94,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0015",
      "text": "particular FC-4, shall be specified in the corresponding FC-4 standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        407.04,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0016",
      "text": "A Process Login remains in effect until a process logout occurs.  The number of concurrent Process",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.03,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0017",
      "text": "Logins in effect at an Nx_Port is a function of the Nx_Port facilities available.  Process Login is sepa-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.01,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0018",
      "text": "rate from N_Port Login.  Process Login may be either implicit or explicit.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        413.14,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0019",
      "text": "There are 2 types of Process Login:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        254.28,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0020",
      "text": "a) Implicit Process Login is a method of establishing an operating environment by means other",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        310.96,
        540.01,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0021",
      "text": "than the explicit use of the PRLI Exchange.  Specific methods of Implicit Process Login are not",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        322.96,
        540.0,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0022",
      "text": "defined in this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        334.96,
        228.47,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0023",
      "text": "b) Explicit Process Login is accomplished by using the PRLI ELS Sequence within a separate Ex-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        358.96,
        540.05,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0024",
      "text": "change to establish an operating environment.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        370.96,
        327.42,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0025",
      "text": "A group of related processes is known as an image and is identified by the Process_Associator (see",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        539.93,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0026",
      "text": "figure 4).  The combination of the D_ID, Responder Process_Associator, S_ID and Originator",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.59,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0027",
      "text": "Process_Associator identify the image pair (see figure 5).  Either a single group or multiple groups of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.88,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0028",
      "text": "related processes may exist behind an Nx_Port.  A single group of related processes behind an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        539.94,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p197_s0029",
      "text": "Nx_Port may be denoted by either an N_Port_ID only or N_Port_ID and Process_Associator.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        506.53,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
